{
  "stem": "11801.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What does he say to a wife he hasn't seen in six years and who comes from a different planet?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her experiences and her, you know, way of life for those six years had been so horrendously difficult that nobody could imagine what it was like.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, I often thought that my experience also was so different from anybody else's.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And certainly all of a sudden being reunited, not only with a mother but with a father-- what do you do with a mother and father?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I was very conditioned to a very authoritarian life, to a very rigid, regimented life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not that I liked it, but I was almost conditioned to, to live in that fashion and to not to really need a father and a mother.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I was grown up by now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was 16, but I felt like as if I was 50.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What, what did I need a mother and a father for?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could take care of myself, if not physically-- I mean, you know, at least I didn't need them to tell me what to do or, or what not to do or when to eat and when not to eat.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't think I needed them for moral support or for emotional support.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- you know, to me, they were--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt very strongly about my mother, at a certain level, because I felt terrible about her experience.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always felt that, if nobody else, I had to make it up to her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had, you know, a very ambivalent feeling about her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At the same time, I had a very difficult time getting along with her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was this very strong, very willful person who had many demands.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
